19 July 2009Members of the media are invited to a media briefing to be addressed by the President of the Republic of South Africa, Mr Jacob Zuma.Date: 19 July 2009 (Sunday) Time: 12:00 Venue: Room 153 (Media Briefing Room), Union Buildings, Pretoria.NB: There will be a video link-up to the Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape Town.Enquiries:Themba Maseko (Government Spokesperson) Cell: 083 645 0810Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)